I"Ÿ<h3 id="sounds-and-alerts">Sounds and Alerts</h3>

<p>Robogotchi will play audio alerts (also referred to as tones or melodies) for various events. Some of these alerts are user configurable using FreeSK8 Mobile.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Startup sound - Mario</li>
  <li>Storage at capacity - Lick</li>
  <li>Bluetooth connection successful - Keyboard Cat</li>
  <li>ESC Fault - NGGYU</li>
  <li>Low Voltage - Lion Sleeps</li>
  <li>ESC Over Temperature - Castlevania</li>
  <li>Motors Over Temperature - Bach</li>
  <li>GPS Signal Acquired - Uplift</li>
  <li>GPS Signal Lost - Disappoint</li>
  <li>Logging started - Ascending</li>
  <li>Logging stopped - Descending</li>
</ul>
